# Ship the COMPLETE test suite in the sdist: setuptools' legacy default
# glob includes tests/test*.py but silently drops conftest.py and
# tests/__init__.py, leaving distro packagers a half-suite that fails
# with "fixture not found" (conftest defines load-bearing fixtures and
# the macOS OMP guards).
recursive-include tests *.py

# Ship the historical record + contributor onramp in the sdist. setuptools
# auto-includes LICENSE + README (via pyproject metadata) but not these,
# so distro packagers and PyPI source-archive readers would otherwise see
# a release with no changelog and no contributing guide.
include CHANGELOG.md
include CONTRIBUTING.md
